data.name: ui_menuOptions_displayAllAssets.ToolTipText
data.value: Check this option will display all types assets. Not extractable assets can export the RAW file.

data.name: ui_menuOptions_enablePreview.ToolTipText
data.value: Toggle the loading and preview of readable assets, such as images, sounds, text, etc. Disable preview if you have performance or compatibility issues.

data.name: ui_menuOptions_displayInfo.ToolTipText
data.value: Toggle the overlay that shows information about each asset, eg. image size, format, audio bitrate, etc.
